contentBody:
Rohan is building a ticket booking system. He writes the following code to determine the ticket price based on age:

```python
age = int(input("Enter age: "))

if age < 5:
    print("Free")
elif age <= 12:
    print("Half Price")
elif age <= 59:
    print("Full Price")
else:
    print("Senior Discount")
```

A user enters **65**. What will be printed?
